data.description: An outstanding opportunity in Harriet Creek with this huge cul-de-sac home. If you are looking for tons of affordable space, you're at the right place. Located in Northwest ISD with a very short drive to restaurants, shopping and entertainment you have all you could want or need close by. Featuring 2 very large living spaces on the first floor, a comfortable open kitchen with ample counter space & storage. Owners suite downstairs is complete with a seating area and plenty of room for your king size bed. The ensuite bath will delight you with a garden tub, separate shower, dual vanity and walk-in closet. Remaining 4 bedrooms are upstairs with two additional bathrooms and more flex space. All new luxury plank floors installed Sept 2023.
